Description: Bebaas Inc. is a California corporation founded in June, 2004 and based in Newport Beach, California.
Headquarters Regions: Greater San Diego Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Bebaas is a California corporation founded in June, 2004 and based in Newport Beach, California. Bebaas is a biopharmaceutical company focused on the discovery, development, and commercialization of novel drug therapies utilizing its patent-pending cobalamin delivery mechanism.  The Company's research has led to the first-ever drug product capable of getting as much cobalamin, vitamin B12, into the bloodstream as an intramuscular injection of vitamin B12, and it maintains those levels longer than the injections. Additionally, it allows for cobalamin to be utilized as either a scavenger or a donor, leaving the door open to virtually limitless drug discovery. Bebaas is developing an internal product pipeline and lead compounds through the application of its proprietary cobalamin delivery technology.  The Company’s drug discovery platform, which has been validated in animal models, is based on the utilization of its patent-pending combinations of various vitamin B12 analogs that generate extremely high cobalamin levels. Numerous API can be added to the cobalamin delivery for oncology, hematology, cardiology, cyanide toxicity, wound healing and other therapeutic applications.  The basis for the research platform has led to the Company’s creation of the first completely non-invasive treatment for pernicious anemia, a cherry-flavored sublingual lozenge, CobacanTM, that has demonstrated in animal models to deliver a far more potent dose than the current standard of care, intramuscular injections of cobalamin.
Industry Groups: Biotechnology, Health Care, Manufacturing, Science and Engineering

Description: SaaS Revenue Acceleration
Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: Keychain Logic provides strategic business planning and executive leadership services to the Software-as-a-Service (SaaS) and On-Demand sectors. We are the only company of our kind that is dedicated to developing the SaaS business model and accelerating SaaS vendors' revenue generation. Our sole purpose is to drive scalable growth in service-focused enterprise software companies. The software industry's transformation to SaaS involves a fundamental shift in independent software vendors' (ISVs') position in their customers' value chain. ISVs no longer are merely application suppliers; they must become trusted advisors, delivering full-service solutions that integrate hardware, network, and software into seamless technology mechanisms that improve essential business processes and add valuable expertise. These differences require ISVs to change how they build, deploy, market, and sell; the starkly dissimilar revenue models mean ISVs need to adjust not only the way they recognize revenue but the speed and efficiency with which they generate it. Keychain Logic's customizable services are based on accepted best practices for technology service providers: Strategic Leadership: Successful SaaS deployments result from robust planning and visionary entrepreneurship. Keychain Logic's interim strategic leadership services provide a cross-functional view and executive-level expertise to companies that are evaluating, developing, launching, and growing their service-focused software business. Executive Search: In the exploding and highly competitive world of SaaS, the right sales & marketing people can mean the difference between an ISV's success or failure. Keychain Logic leverages its expertise and extensive network of industry professionals to identify highly qualified candidates. Incentive Compensation: Designed for subscription- and success-based recurring revenue models, Keychain Logic's high-performance sales compensation plans support the shorter SaaS sales cycle and encourage salespeople to aggressively hunt new business. Lead Generation: Integrating traditional brand marketing with highly cost-effective guerrilla tactics, Keychain Logic's lead generation programs deliver new high quality prospects and percolate them into â€œhotâ€ sales leads. Sales Cycle Management: Keychain Logic's tools and systems stress immediacy in funnel management and significantly shorten sales cycles while increasing closing ratios and allowing SaaS ISVs to serve more customers per account team.
Industry Groups: Internet Services, Professional Services, Sales and Marketing, Software
